{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/06/27/南山博物馆浮世绘展.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5d5d02a8-25f7-5b38-a0b1-3e83a8759008","excerpt":"南山博物馆浮世绘展览 过去一个月基本上每周都去南山文体中心游泳，常常会路过南山博物馆，因为疫情原因，南山博物馆一直是关闭的，直到我看到了浮世绘的海报，从…","html":"<h1>南山博物馆浮世绘展览</h1>\n<p>过去一个月基本上每周都去南山文体中心游泳，常常会路过南山博物馆，因为疫情原因，南山博物馆一直是关闭的，直到我看到了浮世绘的海报，从 6 月份开始南山博物馆开始展览。</p>\n<p>因为疫情还在继续，前往南山博物馆需要提前预约并申报健康码。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/b4294/05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/cbe2e/05.webp 148w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/3084c/05.webp 295w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/5ca24/05.webp 590w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/e88ff/05.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/a80bd/05.jpg 148w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/1c91a/05.jpg 295w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/1c72d/05.jpg 590w,\n/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/b4294/05.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/df706c6530f314f4d04cb134d2e17145/1c72d/05.jpg\"\n          alt=\"南山博物馆入口\"\n          title=\"南山博物馆入口\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">南山博物馆入口</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>浮世绘就是源于日本民间的版画，最早是被荷兰人从包装商品的废纸中翻出来，日本人发现竟然有人稀罕这东西，便也拿出来给西方人卖。</p>\n<h2>主题</h2>\n<p>因为产自民间，浮世绘往往绘画美人、戏曲中的角色、还有春宫图（嘿嘿）。当然，像是风景画什么的也很多见。展览最后说浮世绘影响了西方的印象派绘画，还拿出梵高、莫奈的画来当证据，不过，浙江的博物馆也说水墨画影响了西方印象派…反正都是几百年前的事儿，也没法考证，爱咋咋地吧~</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/b4294/01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 135.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/cbe2e/01.webp 148w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/3084c/01.webp 295w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/5ca24/01.webp 590w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/e88ff/01.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/a80bd/01.jpg 148w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/1c91a/01.jpg 295w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/1c72d/01.jpg 590w,\n/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/b4294/01.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/1311f8692e6d0c25ac940cfd134d1042/1c72d/01.jpg\"\n          alt=\"这春宫图实在是太清水了\"\n          title=\"这春宫图实在是太清水了\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">这春宫图实在是太清水了</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/b4294/03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/cbe2e/03.webp 148w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/3084c/03.webp 295w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/5ca24/03.webp 590w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/e88ff/03.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/a80bd/03.jpg 148w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/1c91a/03.jpg 295w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/1c72d/03.jpg 590w,\n/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/b4294/03.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/fa61c377ebdc1a94ccff2fde415bf734/1c72d/03.jpg\"\n          alt=\"这个也一般\"\n          title=\"这个也一般\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">这个也一般</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/4b190/02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/cbe2e/02.webp 148w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/3084c/02.webp 295w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/5ca24/02.webp 590w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/d00b9/02.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/a80bd/02.jpg 148w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/1c91a/02.jpg 295w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/1c72d/02.jpg 590w,\n/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/4b190/02.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/ed86f07712ae7ef2feed593ea24d8f29/1c72d/02.jpg\"\n          alt=\"本山老师的猪腰子脸在过去可是美人的标准\"\n          title=\"本山老师的猪腰子脸在过去可是美人的标准\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">本山老师的猪腰子脸在过去可是美人的标准</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>六大家</h2>\n<p>擅长绘制嬉戏女性的铃木春信、绘制已婚妇女生活情景的鸟居清长、偏向中国水墨山水画风的哥川广中、绘制美人肖像画的喜多川歌麿、绘制歌舞剧情景的东洲斋写乐以及以神奈川冲浪里出名的葛饰北斋是浮世绘的六大家。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/b4294/04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.78378378378378%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/cbe2e/04.webp 148w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/3084c/04.webp 295w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/5ca24/04.webp 590w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/e88ff/04.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/a80bd/04.jpg 148w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/1c91a/04.jpg 295w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/1c72d/04.jpg 590w,\n/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/b4294/04.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/377d25a1b187900bf3fd0131055c44f1/1c72d/04.jpg\"\n          alt=\"神奈川冲浪里\"\n          title=\"神奈川冲浪里\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">神奈川冲浪里</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>审查制度</h2>\n<p>和水墨画上面的印章不一样，浮世绘上面的印章主要表示它是被谁审查的，就像现在的版号，可以根据这些印章判断版画的出版时间。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/南山博物馆浮世绘展.html","date":"June 27, 2020","title":"南山博物馆浮世绘展"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/南山博物馆浮世绘展.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/24/海南旅行计划.html","title":"海南旅行计划"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/28/珠海横琴线横穿澳门.html","title":"珠海横琴线横穿澳门"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}}}}}